library("ggplot2")
library("ggvega")
## Welcome to ggvega; this package is not yet fully functional, and is under active development.
plot <- 
  ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Width, y = Sepal.Length)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = Species))
  
plot

vl_spec <- as_vegaspec(plot)

vl_spec$width = 300
vl_spec$height = 300

vl_spec
